snippet.textDisplay:
Zeeshan Ali announced a surprise at 2am during the concert in Lahore, and I was curious about what it could be at that night time. But at 2am, I received a notification on YouTube that Coke Studio had uploaded a new song "2AM" by Zeeshan Ali. I was pleasantly surprised! After listening to the song, I was hooked; it's a masterpiece in soft Punjabi, and Zeeshan Ali's intensity is incredible. The lyrics are so meaningful. I've been playing it all day and all night!
here is the clip of that announcement: https://youtu.be/VNg5aD6yQ5w?si=4ODyg2Yw2vuhpRPe&t=488

Writing this just at 2 am
Dear coke studio, believe me, you are literally the pride of the nation as your slogan says. There are very rare good things in our country but the hallmark you guys have set for the world is beyond words. Ahhh what do I say…. There is only one word that comes into my mind when hearing the word coke studio - it’s nothing but pure LOVE. Coke studio is all about love, poetry, harmony - even enemies find love for each other here
